OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782011884
OL,3,CHeatwave threshold likely met at
OL,4,Cweekend before next week's extreme
OL,5,Cheat warning
OL,7,FThe heatwave threshold will likely be
OL,8,Fmet for some at the weekend before the
OL,9,Fweek starts with an amber extreme heat
OL,10,Fwarning, with temperatures potentially
OL,11,Fclimbing up to or above 34C.
OL,13,FThe Met Office warning is in place on
OL,14,FMonday and Tuesday for London, the
OL,15,Feast and south-east of England, and
OL,16,Fparts of the south-west of England and
OL,17,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
