FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782011884
OL,3,CHeatwave threshold likely met at
OL,4,Cweekend before next week's extreme
OL,5,Cheat warning
OL,7,F"Entering it unexpectedly can lead to
OL,8,Fcold water shock, causing a sudden
OL,9,Fincrease in breathing and heart rate,
OL,10,Fwhich may trigger panic."
OL,12,FAfter the heat health alerts were
OL,13,Fissued, the Health and Safety
OL,14,FExecutive (HSE) said employers must
OL,15,Fensure their workers are protected
OL,16,Fwhile maintaining productivity during
OL,17,Fthe heatwave.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@YO]
